{"per_page":10,"total":1,"current":1,"data":[{"title":"关于去设创读研这件事","date":"2021-06-12T18:03:42.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jun 12, 2021","L":"06/12/2021","MM-DD":"06-12"},"excerpt":"","link":"2021/06/12/why-d-and-i","categories":["Life"]},{"title":"[实习小结] 2020日常实习——字节跳动AML团队","date":"2021-06-12T17:36:20.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jun 12, 2021","L":"06/12/2021","MM-DD":"06-12"},"excerpt":"","link":"2021/06/12/bytedance","categories":["Internship"]},{"title":"[实习小结] 2020暑期实习——阿里巴巴数据中台团队","date":"2021-06-12T17:35:16.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Jun 12, 2021","L":"06/12/2021","MM-DD":"06-12"},"excerpt":"<p>毕设做完之后，人终于可以闲下来了。趁这段难得的时间，就想着整理一下自己过去一年发生的事。因为过去一年确确实实是我人生中对我改变最多的一年，无论是从技术上，还是从为人处世上，我感觉自己都得到了很大的提升。所以，本文是这一系列总结的第一篇，先来小结下在阿里实习的经历，之后应该还会分别写两篇文章总结下在字节实习和保研的经历。</p>","link":"2021/06/12/alibaba","categories":["Internship"]},{"title":"[CodeRead] TiDB Lightning","date":"2021-03-19T18:48:44.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 19, 2021","L":"03/19/2021","MM-DD":"03-19"},"excerpt":"<p>TiDB Lightning 是一个将数据导入到 TiDB 中的工具，使用 Go 编写。支持 <code>Local</code>, <code>Importer</code>, <code>TiDB</code> 三种导入模式。在 TiDB 的官网中，对其<a href=\"\">原理</a>有着详细的介绍。</p>\n<p><img src=\"/asset/tidb-lightning/1.png\" alt=\"\" class=\"φbs\"></p>\n<p>本文从代码的角度，带领大家走过一个数据导入的过程，所以只关注一些逻辑上重要的步骤，而一些其他的细节可能不会涉及到。</p>","link":"2021/03/19/tidb-lightning","tags":["TiDB"],"categories":["DB"]},{"title":"[Tutorial] Kubernetes Ramp Up","date":"2021-03-15T15:39:36.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 15, 2021","L":"03/15/2021","MM-DD":"03-15"},"excerpt":"","link":"2021/03/15/k8s-ramp-up","tags":["Kubernetes"],"categories":["Cloud"]},{"title":"[BugFix] Kubernetes Ingress Nginx DNS报错日志 Bug Fix","date":"2021-03-13T12:27:49.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 13, 2021","L":"03/13/2021","MM-DD":"03-13"},"excerpt":"","link":"2021/03/13/ingress-nginx-bug-fix","tags":["Kubernetes"],"categories":["Cloud"]},{"title":"[Introduction] Kubernetes Webhook","date":"2021-03-08T23:47:05.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"Mar 8, 2021","L":"03/0